      <talk_answer link_index="n034_cleric_master_germain-3-a" mid="87"><![CDATA[<html>（解释在森林圣域发生的事）</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="86"><![CDATA[<html>$高级牧师杰梅因$<BR>在森林圣域找到 <FONT color=#a82424>雷安的线索</FONT>了吗?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
